1
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:55,740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

2
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:59,780
=Episode 14=
=Between Gain and Loss=

3
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:04,280
Ding Daang, have you lost your mind?

4
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:05,920
You called off the engagement?

5
00:01:06,700 --> 00:01:07,560
Do you even realize

6
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,800
the deadline for the legacy

7
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:09,840
is coming up soon?

8
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,160
If you cancel it now,

9
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:13,200
your dad's money will all be donated.

10
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,480
We won't get a single cent.

11
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,280
You don't get to control my marriage.

12
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,540
Yes.

13
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:20,880
I don't want to interfere either.

14
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,840
I'm just giving you a heads-up.

15
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,840
Don't throw yourself away

16
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:26,160
over people who don't matter.

17
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,760
And now you've even dragged me into it.

18
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,800
While it's within the deadline,

19
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,280
get married.

20
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:34,160
Marriage is just a label.

21
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,400
Liu Xiaoting.

22
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,840
Don't think I don't know

23
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,080
the little game you're playing.

24
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:43,560
So what if you know?

25
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,640
Love isn't enough to live on.

26
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:48,080
Without money, you're nothing.

27
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:50,220
Ding Daang, don't forget.

28
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:53,400
He's the one who left you back then.

29
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,680
If this engagement falls through,

30
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,440
you won't get a cent.

31
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,160
By then, you'll truly have nothing.

32
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,360
I've had nothing for a long time.

33
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:13,040
From the day you betrayed my dad.

34
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:19,720
I caught you, didn't I?

35
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,080
You've got some nerve, Liu Xiaoting.

36
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:29,880
Bringing some random guy

37
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,720
into the house.

38
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:31,570
No.

39
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,720
He's my cousin.

40
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,600
That's my cousin.

41
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:40,920
Cousin?

42
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,800
Hey.

43
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,240
What are you doing, Ding Daang?

44
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,980
Aren't you into tearing people's clothes off?

45
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:52,720
I can help you.

46
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,640
Stop it.

47
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,200
You want it, right?

48
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,440
Twenty thousand.

49
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,720
Give me twenty grand.

50
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,560
Then I'll delete the video.

51
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,880
Or I'll hand it over to my dad.

52
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,760
Have him throw you

53
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:22,840
out of the house.

54
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,240
So what?

55
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:29,440
You were worried I'd tell on you
about you paying

56
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,880
for Chen Aming's mom's treatment.

57
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,920
So you kept my affair

58
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,320
from your dad, didn't you?

59
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,760
Otherwise, how would he die of anger?

60
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,660
You're partly to blame too.

61
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,760
Shut your mouth!

62
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,960
Have you lost it, Ding Daang?

63
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:47,280
I'm using your dad's money
to keep some guy.

64
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,120
Aren't you using your dad's money

65
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,200
to keep a guy as well?

66
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,760
What's the difference?

67
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,000
Hand me the money.

68
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,240
I'll take it and leave.

69
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,960
I don't want to stick around
watching your attitude.

70
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,400
Let's make a deal,

71
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:42,160
Yu Kun.

72
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,400
What kind of deal?

73
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,880
My dad left a will before he passed.

74
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,240
I have to get married.

75
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:09,080
Only then can I get 30% of the estate.

76
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,280
If I stay married each year,

77
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,600
I can get another 10%.

78
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,360
But Liu Xiaoting

79
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,840
has the right to live
in this house permanently.

80
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,880
Unless she chooses to move out.

81
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,760
I made a deal with her.

82
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,160
I'll give her five million.

83
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,760
Then she'll leave.

84
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,120
So?

85
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,720
So I need your help.

86
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,000
When it's done,

87
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,560
I'll use the legacy
to invest in your app.

88
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,860
Enough for you to keep it operated.

89
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,320
All I need is just a marriage

90
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,280
in name only.

91
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,240
Invest in a selfish guy like me.

92
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,040
Are you serious?

93
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,360
It's just mutual benefit.

94
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,640
I'm exhausted.

95
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,960
You should go.

96
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,360
Alright.

97
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,120
I agree.

98
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,280
Let me go.

99
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,200
What do you think I am?

100
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,360
I take good care of my sponsor.

101
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,040
Any issues?

102
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:20,880
I'm warning you.

103
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,980
You're crossing the line.

104
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,680
I'll draft the contract terms.

105
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,920
Mr. Yu, I hope you and I

106
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,360
can be perfect partners.

107
00:07:42,850 --> 00:07:43,990
Nice doing business with you.

108
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,040
Miss Ding.

109
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:16,140
(Ding Haishan left nearly ten billion
in legacy.)

110
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:17,290
(Ding Daang must be married)

111
00:08:17,290 --> 00:08:19,290
(to receive 30% of the assets.)

112
00:08:19,290 --> 00:08:21,290
(Each year without divorce,
she gets another 10%.)

113
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:24,140
(Liu Xiaoting only has permanent
residence rights for the house.)

114
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,040
How did you get in?

115
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,240
Just a small code lock.

116
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,120
Easy enough.

117
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,640
Sorry, I took a sip of your wine.

118
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:57,640
No problem.

119
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,280
With me, you can do anything.

120
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,360
Relax.

121
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,120
With me, you can do

122
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,000
anything.

123
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,600
Then is it okay if I die here?

124
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,200
Shut it.

125
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,760
Didn't you say I can...?

126
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:32,080
I said zip it.

127
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,840
Don't...

128
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,040
I refuse.

129
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,120
You know.

130
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,840
I grew up an orphan.

131
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,880
I spent years abroad as a hacker.

132
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,400
I even served time.

133
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:10,440
He's the one who spotted my talent

134
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,720
and gave me a way to survive.

135
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,880
He always seemed distant.

136
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,760
But he was the first to treat me kindly.

137
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:23,320
I just want him happy every day.

138
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:26,200
I don't want him to be like this.

139
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:29,080
But if something really happens to him,

140
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,400
who would care about me then?

141
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,120
Me.

142
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,360
We don't actually know each other that well.

143
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:41,360
Anyway, you can't die.

144
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,800
Why not?

145
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:44,880
You still owe me money.

146
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:03,360
Boss.

147
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,200
Let's talk.

148
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:08,840
If you're here to tell me to stop,

149
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,440
don't bother.

150
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,240
No, I'm asking you

151
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,680
to wake up.

152
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:16,160
Your plan's strayed
from our original intentions.

153
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,000
Original intentions?

154
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,640
What was our original goal again?

155
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,800
To get Hu Yitong and Miaomiao together

156
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,960
and our software development
back on track.

157
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,640
That's why you came back, remember?

158
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,600
Not to get tangled up with Ding Daang.

159
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,280
You think Miaomiao would listen to me?

160
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,360
Of course she would.

161
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:37,240
As long as you genuinely take her side

162
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,560
instead of using her.

163
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,800
I know what I'm doing right now.

164
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,760
No need for you to remind me.

165
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,000
You and Ding Daang

166
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,720
were nothing more than a show.

167
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,160
If you let yourself sink deeper,

168
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,880
it'll only make everyone miserable.

169
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,400
Focus on Hu Yitong and Miaomiao.

170
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,720
Let them settle their own grudges.

171
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,200
As for Ding Daang,

172
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:03,520
stop stirring up...

173
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,520
I know.

174
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,360
I'll let them end up together.

175
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:13,440
As for my contract marriage
with Ding Daang,

176
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:15,800
it will go on as planned.

177
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:20,680
Hu Yitong is after Ding Daang's legacy.

178
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,560
Miaomiao wants Hu Yitong.

179
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,880
I'm changing the game plan.

180
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,480
I want everyone

181
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,560
to get what they deserve.

182
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,280
In this scene,

183
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,640
no one gets to walk away early.

184
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:49,460
(Suga Love)

185
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,080
Ding Daang,

186
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,440
where should we hang this photo?

187
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,280
Put it somewhere everyone can see.

188
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,640
Okay.

189
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,640
Ding Daang...

190
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,240
Maybe...

191
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:08,040
we should hang it up later.

192
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:22,240
Ding Daang,

193
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,200
can we talk?

194
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,320
Hu Yitong,

195
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,720
our deal is over.

196
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:30,960
Excuse me.

197
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:34,920
I know I messed up.

198
00:13:35,700 --> 00:13:36,990
Please, give me one more chance.

199
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,920
I... I swear.

200
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,240
Ding Daang.

201
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,440
President Hu.

202
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,360
Going after

203
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,920
someone else's fiancée openly

204
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:49,680
isn't classy, right?

205
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:53,480
Oh, by the way,

206
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,440
we're married now.

207
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,590
We just got registered for marriage.

208
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:01,240
Take a look.

209
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:14,440
Boss, Miaomiao is about to hurt herself.

210
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:40,840
Tell me, am I stupid?

211
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,760
I had everything planned,

212
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,800
but my heart still aches so much.

213
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:51,760
Every single thing,

214
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:54,920
the time, the place, the gifts...

215
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,120
You remembered them perfectly.

216
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,320
Like you memorized a textbook.

217
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:03,040
But I can't feel any care
from you anymore.

218
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,160
Water.

219
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:09,120
I need some water.

220
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:50,500
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

221
00:15:54,900 --> 00:16:02,260
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

222
00:16:06,710 --> 00:16:08,650
♪They say♪

223
00:16:09,060 --> 00:16:17,440
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

224
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:20,940
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

225
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:27,110
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

226
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:34,250
♪I've already lost you♪

227
00:16:34,250 --> 00:16:39,730
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

228
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:45,980
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

229
00:16:45,980 --> 00:16:50,760
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

230
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:55,900
♪The past will always pass♪

231
00:16:56,230 --> 00:17:03,810
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

232
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:07,530
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

233
00:17:08,090 --> 00:17:13,740
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

234
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:19,730
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

235
00:17:19,730 --> 00:17:25,990
♪But sadly, it's not you♪
